### OLD PLACES API (pre-2023) EXAMPLES
##########################################

### 1. Autocomplete (Old) - Basic search
GET https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/place/autocomplete/json?input=Ramabharathi&key={{apiKey}}&components=country:in
Accept: application/json

### 2. Autocomplete (Old) - Search with location bias
GET https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/place/autocomplete/json?input=restaurant&location=28.6139,77.2090&radius=5000&components=country:in&key={{apiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### 3. Place Details (Old) - Basic place details
GET https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/place/details/json?place_id=ChIJj61dQgK6j4AR4GeTYWZsKWw&fields=place_id,name,formatted_address,geometry/location&key={{apiKey}}
Accept: application/json

